headline: Inside the private equity firm giving new life to Chef Boyardee, Pillsbury
summary: Brynwood Partners purchases well-known brands that have fallen out of favor with large CPG manufacturers, then boosts marketing and innovation to rejuvenate sales, says CEO Henk Hartong.
